{"tid":2347462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"強烈要求香港政府，嚴懲呢對由中國偷渡來港情侶","createTime":"2020-12-31T05:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T05:49:12.000Z","uid":134093,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"15a3108687ee5dd54049393ff75ae4561c57c123","tid":2347462,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:16:19.000Z","msg":"以12港人案為例<br />\n呢對情侶涉嫌觸犯跨越邊境罪，及組織他人跨越邊境罪<br />\n嚴重危害國家安全，傷害14億中國同胞感情<br />\n<br />\n強烈要求香港政府以港區國安法懲處呢對情侶<br />\n以保障一國兩制，安定繁榮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水警昨晚（28日）約7時在青山龍鼓灘一帶進行打擊非法入境行動，行動中警員在龍鼓灘一沙灘拘捕一名32歲內地男子及一名35歲內地女子非法入境，其中該名男子同時涉嫌「協助及教唆他人非法入境」被捕，案件交由水警總區重案組跟進，所有被捕男女現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201229/55O7SI7AFNBHJAL4Z6QGJZIKBE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR01DJ0GNHFkskjiS1c60TItZ7jVAwbpGuoZoeDv9FHY4DBSr6OhzlgSzlo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201229%2F55O7SI7AFNBHJAL4Z6QGJZIKBE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR01DJ0GNHFkskjiS1c60TItZ7jVAwbpGuoZoeDv9FHY4DBSr6OhzlgSzlo&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=7aac38de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201229%2F55O7SI7AFNBHJAL4Z6QGJZIKBE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR01DJ0GNHFkskjiS1c60TItZ7jVAwbpGuoZoeDv9FHY4DBSr6OhzlgSzlo&h=ad676559\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201229/55O7SI7AFNBHJAL4Z6QGJZIKBE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbcli